#Constants explained

#The definition of a variable is:
#A named location
#In a computers memory
#that stores a value
#the value can change

#The definition of a CONSTANCE is:
#A named location
#In a computers memory
#that stores a value
#the value SHOULD NOT be changed

#Here is an example of a CONSTANT
FREETHROW = 1
DUNKSHOT = 2
THREEPOINTER = 3
numberOfFouls = 0#this is a variable as it is not in capital letters so you don't change it
